                "invention-title": [
                    "System and process for preparing synthesis gas through reaction of carbon dioxide and hydrogen",
                    "用于二氧化碳和氢气反应制备合成气的系统及工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a system and process for preparing synthesis gas through reaction of carbon dioxide and hydrogen, the system comprises n stages of reverse water vapor shift units which are sequentially connected in series, n is greater than or equal to 3, and the system is used for sequentially performing n stages of reverse water vapor shift reaction on fed CO2 and H2 to obtain the synthesis gas. According to the process, carbon dioxide and hydrogen are subjected to an n-stage reverse water vapor shift reaction by using the system, and synthesis gas is obtained; a catalyst used in the n-stage reverse water vapor shift reaction is a Cr2O3/MgAl2O4-TiO2 catalyst; the Cr2O3/MgAl24-TiO2 catalyst is a catalyst formed by loading Cr2O3 on a MgAl2O4 spinel carrier modified by TiO2, and the MgAl2O4 spinel carrier modified by TiO2 is used as the catalyst. The system does not need to be provided with a circulating pipeline, a decarburization device and a hydrogen separation device; according to the system and the process, CO2 and H2 can be efficiently converted into synthesis gas on a large scale, and the requirements of subsequent synthesis of high-added-value chemicals and oil products are met; the reaction temperature is low."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种用于二氧化碳和氢气反应制备合成气的系统及工艺，系统包括依次串联设置的n级逆水汽变换单元，n≥3，用于对进料CO2和H2依次进行n级逆水汽变换反应获得合成气。所述工艺利用前述系统使二氧化碳和氢气进行n级逆水汽变换反应，得到合成气；所述n级逆水汽变换反应中所用催化剂为Cr2O3/MgAl2O4‑TiO2催化剂；Cr2O3/MgAl2O4‑TiO2催化剂是Cr2O3负载在TiO2修饰的MgAl2O4尖晶石载体上形成的催化剂。该系统无需设置循环管路、脱炭装置以及分氢装置；该系统及工艺可以实现CO2和H2高效规模化转化为合成气，满足后续合成高附加值化学品和油品的需要；反应温度低。"
                }
            ]
